text: Renn ir'Tanar is a powerful and influential [[warlord|Karrnathi warlord]] of [[Karrnath]], and lord of the fortress-town [[Tanar Rath]]. While he publicly supports King [[Kaius ir'Wynarn III]], he secretly leads efforts to derail peacemaking efforts and restart the [[Last War]].
title: Renn ir'Tanar
tooltip: powerful and influential warlord of Karrnath, lord of Tanar Rath
